Package HdbOfficer

Class HdbOfficerRepo

java.lang.Object
HdbOfficer.HdbOfficerRepo
All Implemented Interfaces:
UserRepo<HdbOfficer>
public class HdbOfficerRepo extends Object implements UserRepo<HdbOfficer>
Repository class to manage HDB Officers. Handles loading and saving officer data from/to a CSV file, and provides methods to interact with officer records.
